resources.string: This application is project for class Programming mobile applications, on Faculty of Technical Sciences in Čačak. Creator of this app is Branislav Radojević, index 47/2019. Purpose of this app is to show astronauts orbiting Earth at this moment. In Earth\'s orbit there are two space station: ISS(International Space Station) and Shenzhou 15.

Ova aplikacija je rađena u okviru predmeta Programiranje mobilnih aplikacija, na Fakultetu tehničkih nauka u Čačku. Kreator ove aplikacije je Branislav Radojević, indeksa 47/2019. Svrha ove aplikacije je da prikaže astronaute koji se nalaze u Zemljinoj orbiti. U orbiti se trenutno nalaze dve svemirske stanice: ISS (International Space Station) i Shenzhou 15.
